# Electron Forge's packaging preflight requires pnpm to declare a hoist
# configuration. `hoist-pattern[]=*` is pnpm's DEFAULT internal hoisting
# (into the virtual store, node_modules/.pnpm/node_modules) made explicit —
# direct dependencies stay strictly isolated, so undeclared imports still
# fail, and the packaged app is unaffected (it ships the bundled .vite
# output plus explicitly copied native modules; see forge.config.ts).
hoist-pattern[]=*
